OL,4,Cscript made actor 'scream out loud'
OL,6,FGavin and Stacey star Melanie Walters
OL,7,Fsaid one moment in the festive script
OL,8,Fmade her "scream out loud" when she
OL,9,Fread through for the first time.
OL,11,FWalters, who plays Stacey's mother,
OL,12,FGwen West, said: "When it came through
OL,13,Fthe post I had, of course, conjured up
OL,14,Fmany a possible storyline, none of
OL,15,Fwhich came close to what was written.
OL,17,F"Our director Chris Gernon had warned
OL,18,Fme that there would be a moment that,
OL,19,Fwhen reading the script, I would
OL,20,Fscream out loud and she was right."
