OL,6,FThe 46-year-old said the script for
OL,7,Fthe sitcom's final episode made him
OL,8,Flaugh and cry, and said the finished
OL,9,Fproduct "hasn't disappointed".
OL,11,F"I want to say I was nervous about
OL,12,Freading the script as it's always been
OL,13,FRuth (Jones') and James (Corden's)
OL,14,Fpriority to get the script perfect in
OL,15,Fthe first instance, to tell a story
OL,16,Fthe right way," he said.
