OL,6,F"(The script) made me laugh, it made
OL,7,Fme cry and upon completion, I thought
OL,8,Fit was nothing short of a
OL,9,Fmasterpiece," Horne said, "not just in
OL,10,Fterms of an episode of Gavin And
OL,11,FStacey, but frankly any script I've
OL,12,Fever read."
OL,14,FSpeaking about crafting the script, co-
OL,15,Fwriter Ruth Jones, who also plays
OL,16,FVanessa "Nessa" Jenkins, added: "It
OL,17,Fwas a mixture of excitement, nostalgia
OL,18,Fand sadness.
