OL,6,F"Sad of course because this is the
OL,7,Flast time these characters will ever
OL,8,Fbe on screen again, but so exciting to
OL,9,Fbring them to life again," she said,
OL,10,F"And nostalgic because we'd be on set
OL,11,Fwith the cast and we'd go down memory
OL,12,Flane remembering the early episodes.
OL,14,F"We often reminisced about Maggie John
OL,15,F(who played Doris O'Neill) who is no
OL,16,Flonger with us, but we felt she was in
OL,17,Fspirit, especially when we were on
OL,18,FTrinity Street."
