OL,6,F"For the 2019 Christmas special and on
OL,7,Fthis finale, we had a film crew
OL,8,Ffollowing the entire time. It's very
OL,9,Femotional watching everybody because
OL,10,Fthe very last thing that we shot is
OL,11,Fthe very last moment of the show.
OL,13,F"So there were a lot of tears that day
OL,14,Fand I hope that people that like the
OL,15,Fshow will enjoy getting a little
OL,16,Fglimpse into it."
