OL,6,FThe hit TV series aired between 2007
OL,7,Fand 2010 and returned in 2019 with a
OL,8,Fone-off festive special, which ended
OL,9,Fon a cliffhanger when Nessa proposed
OL,10,Fto Corden's character, Smithy.
OL,12,FGavin And Stacey: The Finale will air
OL,13,Fat 9pm on Christmas Day on BBC One and
OL,14,FiPlayer. The documentary Gavin And
OL,15,FStacey: A Fond Farewell will be shown
OL,16,Fat 7pm on New Year's Day on BBC One
OL,17,Fand iPlayer.
